ğŸ§± Method 2: Flatpak (Recommended for Mint)

Flatpak runs Teams in a sandbox, works well with Mintâ€™s Cinnamon desktop, and avoids repo issues.

Install Flatpak & Teams:
sudo apt install -y flatpak
sudo flatpak install flathub com.microsoft.Teams -y

Run Teams:
flatpak run com.microsoft.Teams

Update later:
flatpak update

ğŸŒ Method 3: Browser-based PWA (Fastest + Lightest)

